---

## 2. Target Audience

- Gym-goers and weightlifters (beginners → advanced)
- People who want to track strength training progress over time
- Fitness enthusiasts looking for AI-powered coaching and workout analysis
- Gen-Z / Millennial demographic (app tone, humor, Aura feature)

---

## 3. Subscription Tiers & Pricing

RepAI uses a **reverse trial + hybrid monetization** model:

| Tier | Price | Duration | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| **Pro Trial** | **Free** | 14 days | New users get ALL Pro features free for 14 days (reverse trial). No credit card required. |
| **Free** | **$0** | Forever | After trial expires, the app still works with core features. Limited functionality. |
| **Pro (Lifetime)** | **~$4.99** (one-time) | Forever | One-time purchase. Unlocks all local/offline Pro features permanently. |
| **AI Subscriber** | **Monthly subscription ~$14.99** | Recurring | Everything in Pro **plus** AI Coach, Cloud Sync, Cloud Backup, Workout Aura. Requires account creation. |

> **Billing Provider:** RevenueCat (wrapping Google Play Billing).  
> **Entitlements:** `RepAI Pro` (one-time), `RepAI AI` (monthly subscription).  
> **Offerings:** `pro_lifetime`, `ai_monthly`.

---

## 4. Feature Breakdown by Tier

### 4.1 Features Available to ALL Users (Free Tier Included)

These features remain accessible **forever**, even after the 14-day trial expires:

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| **Workout Logging** | Start a workout session, name it, add exercises, log sets (weight × reps) in real time |
| **Exercise Library** | Browse a built-in library of exercises organized by muscle group and category (strength, cardio, flexibility) |
| **Custom Exercises** | Create your own exercises with custom name, category, and muscle group |
| **Workout History** | View all past workouts with full details (exercises, sets, volume, duration, notes) |
| **Progress Charts** | Visualize exercise progress over time with charts for Max Weight, Total Volume, and Best Set |
| **Workout Programs** | Browse built-in training programs filterable by level (beginner/intermediate/advanced) and goal (strength/hypertrophy/general/fat loss) with detailed day-by-day breakdowns |
| **Weekly Stats Dashboard** | Home screen shows weekly sessions count, total sets, minutes, and volume (kg) |
| **Lifetime Stats** | Total workouts, total sets, total volume lifted — all time |
| **Session Timer** | Live workout duration timer during active sessions |
| **Rest Timer** | Configurable rest timer between sets with header badge countdown |
| **Session Notes** | Add notes to individual workouts |
| **Mood/Energy Tracking** | Rate energy level (1–5 emoji scale) per workout |
| **Body Stats** | Track weight (kg), height (cm), and body fat (%) |
| **Localization** | Full app in 5 languages with RTL support |
| **Dark/Light Theme** | User-selectable appearance mode |
| **Personal Records** | Automatic PR detection for Max Weight, Best Volume, and Estimated 1RM with celebration animations |
| **Restore Purchases** | Restore previous purchases after reinstalling |

### 4.2 Pro-Only Features (Locked After Trial)

These features are accessible during the **14-day trial** and require a **Pro Lifetime** purchase or **AI Subscription** after the trial expires:

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| **Body Measurements** | Track 7 body measurements over time: neck, chest, waist, hips, biceps, thighs, calves (cm). Includes history with change indicators (↑/↓). |
| **Supersets / Circuits / Giant Sets** | Link 2+ exercises into supersets, circuits, or giant sets with visual grouping, colored sidebars, and position labels |
| **CSV Export** | Export all workout data as CSV (Date, Time, Workout Name, Exercise, Set #, Weight, Reps, Volume, Notes) via native share sheet |
| **RPE Tracking** | Log Rate of Perceived Exertion (1–10) per set with color-coded badges |
| **Workout Aura** (requires AI account) | Post-workout AI-generated "aura card" — a funny, shareable summary of the workout with stats, sharable as an image |

### 4.3 AI Subscriber–Only Features

Available **only** with an active AI monthly subscription + Clerk account:

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| **AI Coach Chat** | Full conversational AI assistant (powered by OpenAI GPT-5.1 / GPT-4o-mini with dynamic model routing). Has access to the user's complete workout history, PRs, body measurements, and profile. Provides data-driven advice, program suggestions, progress analysis, plateau detection, nutrition guidance. |
| **Smart Model Routing** | Automatically classifies user messages as SIMPLE or COMPLEX and routes to the appropriate AI model (cheap for quick questions, powerful for deep analysis) — optimizes cost while maintaining quality. |
| **Workout Aura** | AI-generated post-workout summary card with 3 character modes: Default (witty), Gym Bro (roast mode), Couch Potato (passive-aggressive). Shareable as image to social media. Includes workout stats overlay. |
| **Cloud Sync** | All workout data is synced to the cloud (Convex) in real-time. Data persists across devices and reinstalls. |
| **Cloud Backup** | Workouts, exercise logs, sets, personal records, body measurements, and custom exercises are all backed up server-side. |
| **Paginated Cloud History** | History screen loads workouts from the cloud with infinite scroll pagination (vs. local-only for free users). |
| **AI Onboarding** | Guided onboarding flow to create a Clerk account, enter profile details (name, DOB, gender, weight, height, body fat, fitness goal), and migrate local data to the cloud. |
| **Fitness Goal Personalization** | Set and update a fitness goal in Settings that the AI uses to tailor all advice. |
| **Subscription Management** | Manage/cancel subscription directly from Settings via Google Play. |
| **Account Management** | Sign out, or permanently delete account and all cloud data. |

