## 5. Monetization Flow

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    NEW USER INSTALLS                 │
│                                                      │
│   ┌──────────────┐                                   │
│   │  14-Day Pro   │  All Pro features unlocked       │
│   │    Trial      │  No signup required               │
│   └──────┬───────┘                                   │
│          │ Trial expires                             │
│          ▼                                           │
│   ┌──────────────┐                                   │
│   │   Free Tier   │  Core features still work        │
│   │              │  Pro features locked               │
│   └──────┬───────┘                                   │
│          │                                           │
│    ┌─────┴──────┐                                    │
│    ▼            ▼                                    │
│ ┌────────┐  ┌──────────────┐                         │
│ │Pro ~$5 │  │ AI Monthly   │                         │
│ │Lifetime│  │ Subscription │                         │
│ │        │  │              │                         │
│ │Local   │  │ Everything   │                         │
│ │features│  │ in Pro PLUS  │                         │
│ │forever │  │ AI + Cloud   │                         │
│ └────────┘  └──────────────┘                         │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Revenue Streams

| Stream | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| **Pro Lifetime** | One-time purchase (~$4.99) | Unlocks all local features forever. No recurring revenue. |
| **AI Subscription** | Monthly recurring | Higher ARPU. Requires Clerk account. Includes server-side costs (OpenAI API, Convex hosting). |

### Upsell Strategy

- Trial banner on Home screen during the 14-day trial (shows days remaining)
- Paywall screen when trial expires or when user taps locked features
- Pro users see an "Upgrade to AI" upsell in Settings
- AI tab shows a dedicated gate screen with feature highlights for non-subscribers

