## 9. Cost Structure (Recurring)

| Cost | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| **OpenAI API** | Variable | Smart routing minimizes this. ~$0.00002 per classification + $0.01–$0.03 per chat response. Aura generation per workout. |
| **Convex Hosting** | Variable | Serverless — scales with active AI subscribers. Free tier covers low usage. |
| **Clerk Auth** | Per-MAU | Only AI subscribers create accounts. |
| **RevenueCat** | Revenue share or flat | Manages all billing/entitlements. |
| **Google Play** | 15–30% commission | Standard store fee on all purchases. |

